Subject: [PATCH 0937/1543] MLK-9719-2 ARM: dts: imx6qdl-sabreauto: change
 disp_id to 1 for HDMI

commit 4af1e75124bc3998a816141f4e83e6f3bca0128f from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git

disp_id 0 is already used for LDB.
The patch fixed the conflict and supported both in one dts file.

Signed-off-by: Robby Cai <r63905@freescale.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi
index 35f70ee..e992cd3 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi
@@ -921,7 +921,7 @@
 
